qbittorrent.name: qbittorrent
qbittorrent.app_readme:
qBittorrent is a cross-platform free and open-source BitTorrent client (Liveness/Readiness/Startup port changed from 8080 to 80)

This App is supplied by TrueCharts, for more information visit the manual: https://truecharts.org/charts/stable/qbittorrent

TrueCharts can only exist due to the incredible effort of our staff. Please consider making a donation or contributing back to the project any way you can!
